articles.title: RCB Stars To Make Debut, Ruturaj Gaikwad Out! India's Likely Playing XI For 3rd ODI Against South Africa - Times Now
articles.description: India will face South Africa in the third ODI of the ongoing three-match series at Boland Park in Paarl on Thursday (December 21). India and South Africa have both won one match each in the series, and so the winner of the third ODI will seal the ODI series. …
